description: Try our easy to follow Breakfast Ham & Egg Cups recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Breakfast Ham & Egg Cups Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Bake for 20 minutes or until egg is just set or cooked to your liking. Stand for 5 minutes before removing from pan. Serve with chargrilled bread and salad leaves.
